      <title>中国建筑商世茂破产清算案被法院驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chinese-builder-shimao-s-liquidation-case-is-dismissed-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世茂集团控股有限公司赢得香港法院的判决，驳回了债权人要求清算这家违约中国开发商的申请，为其完成债务重组计划争取了更多时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chinese-builder-shimao-s-liquidation-case-is-dismissed-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 03:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
